HEADWORD: Ingenuousness
<hw>In*gen"u*ous*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state or
quality of being ingenuous; openness of heart; frankness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

